Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不懂的事情，你自然會多加小心\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}It ain't what you don't know that gets you into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.94,0:01:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,惹禍上身的是你自以為懂的事 -馬克吐溫\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}It's what you know for sure that just ain't so.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.94,0:01:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,（淹死的都是會水的）\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Mark Twain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.14,0:01:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,弗蘭克，老婆孩子還好吧？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Hi ya Frank, how are the wife and kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你考慮過買國庫券或事業公司股票嗎？抽煙嗎\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}you know, shouldn't y'all be considering treasury bonds or utility stocks? Smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.26,0:01:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,在70年代後期\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}in the late seventies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.71,0:01:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,銀行業並不是賺大錢的行業\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}banking wasn't a job you went into to make large sums of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.06,0:01:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對廢柴行業！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}It was a fucking snooze!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.43,0:01:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,到處是窮鬼！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Filled with losers!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,都是來賣保險，做帳的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Like selling insurance, or.... accounting
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果銀行業廢柴的話\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And if banking was boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,證券部門就是植物人呆的地方\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}then the bond department at the bank was straight up comatose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大夥都知道證券是怎麼回事\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}We all know about bonds....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,把證券當禮物送給你的15歲小屁孩\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You give em to your snot nosed kid when he turns fifteen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,到他30了，能拿到一百來塊錢\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Maybe when he's thirty he makes a hundred bucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,累不累啊？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,千呼萬喚，所羅門兄弟公司的劉易斯駕臨\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}That is until Lewis Rainieri came on the scene at Salomon Brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這名不經傳的人物，對你的影響…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You might not know who he is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,比起喬丹、iPod、視頻網站加起來還要大！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}But he changed your life more than Michael Jordan, the I-Pod and Youtube put together!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,先生們，咱們一起發財吧！怎麼樣？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Hey Gentlemen, let's get some money in here. Let's make some money! What do you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可能當時劉易斯還不知道 但其實他已經改變了歷史\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You see, Lewis didn't know it yet, but he already changed banking forever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.96,0:02:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就用最簡單的這個點子\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}with one simple idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,房貸證券(MBS)\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}The mortgage backed security.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,或者私營房貸證券\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}or... Private Label MBS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.07,0:02:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你們都背著普通的房貸\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You got your average persons mortgage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,固定利率，30年還清，沒意思！ 定額小筆錢償還，就這樣了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}fixed rate, thirty years, boring! Same, small payoff. Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}But......
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你把上千個房貸打包起來\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}when you add thousands of them all bundled together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,忽然回報率上升了，但風險還很小\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}suddenly, the yield goes up, but the risk is still small, because....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,因為它們是房貸，哪個神經病不還房貸呢？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Well, they're mortgages, and who the hell doesn't pay their mortgage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.65,0:02:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,這種證券評級怎麼樣？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}What exactly is the credit-rating on this bond?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,證券評級…是AAA級別！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}This bond gentlemen... Is AAA-Rating!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是我們密西根州養老基金一直找的啊！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}This is exactly what the Michigan State Pension fund has been looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我買兩千萬！- 別掃興啊，放開點！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I'll buy twenty million! -Oh come on, live a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,兩千五百萬！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Twenty five million!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,錢就像下雨一樣來了！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}The money came raining down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,銀行家破例從鄉村俱樂部跑到了脫衣舞夜總會\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And for the first time, the banker went from the country-club to the strip-club.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,很快，股票和存款都沒人考慮了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Pretty soon, stocks and savings were almost inconsequential.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,每年大夥都買賣5百億，1千億，2千億的房貸證券\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}They were doing fifty, a hundred, two hundred billion in mortgage bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,還有幾十種其他證券\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}and dozens of other securities a year.
