Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.97,0:03:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一切轟然倒塌\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}It all came crashing down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,貝爾斯登公司陷入泥潭，美聯儲幫忙救急\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Bear Stearns was in a death spiral and the FED brokered it's sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,現代歷史上最嚴重的經濟危機\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}The worst financial crisis in modern times
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,幾十年以來最大的金融海嘯\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}The largest financial disaster in decades
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,很可能是整個時代最糟的情況了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And perhaps the end of the era
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,5百萬人丟了工作\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}5 million unemployed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,到最後，劉易斯的房貸證券 異變成了摧毀全球經濟的怪物\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}In the end Lewis Rainier's mortgage backed security mutated into a monstrosity that collapsed the whole world economy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,專家、領導人或者電視上的權威都沒能預料到\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And none of the experts, or leaders, or talking heads had a clue it was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.06,0:04:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,*驅逐通知\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*Eviction Restoration Notice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我估計你們也沒弄明白髮生了什麼事情\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}and I'm guessing most of you still don't really know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，大家也就是人云亦云一下…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Yeah, you got a sound bite you repeat so you don't sound dumb, but come on....
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,(美國財政部長）我們的金融機構是強有力的！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}(Henry Paulson) Our financial institutions are strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不過確實有人預料到這事兒發生\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}But there were some who saw it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,整個世界都在虛假狂歡 少數的局外人和怪才卻獨具慧眼\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}While the whole world was having a big old party, few outsiders and weirdos saw what no-one else could.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我，我才不怪呢，等會再跟你說我的酷事兒\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Not me, I'm not a weirdo, I'm pretty fucking cool, but... we'll meet again later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.17,0:04:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這些人發現了經濟中心的彌天大謊\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}These outsiders saw the giant lie at the heart of the economy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,方法不難，只是隨大流的人永遠不會去做：\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}and they saw it by doing something the rest of the suckers never thought to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,親自去了解\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}They looked
