Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.15,0:27:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼·摩西，是這群人裡的樂天派\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And Danny Moses, the optimist of the bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.08,0:27:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他是交易鬼才 也這是大夥容忍他傻瓜式樂天派的唯一原因\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And a hell of a trader, which is the only reason they put up with his bullshit optimism.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.38,0:27:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,夥計，你對打錯電話的也太客氣了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You're a weird caller, you take longer with a wrong number than anybody else
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.52,0:27:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙是德意志銀行的，說什麼做空房貸證券\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I mean... it's this guy... from... Deutsche, who was talking about shorting housing bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.60,0:28:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,說到中間，我才聽出他找錯人了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And then, in the middle of the call where I had realized he had the wrong front-point.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.19,0:28:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,然後他說想要找8層的那個公司\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}and then... and then... cause he wanted the one on the eighth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.24,0:28:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他想要做空房貸證券？- 嗯\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}He wanted to short housing bonds? - Hmmm
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.28,0:28:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,每天至少5個撥錯的電話\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}-It happens like five times a day, that somebody uses the wrong front-point.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.79,0:28:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,咱們得改個名了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}We should change our name!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.42,0:28:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等，他想要做空房貸證券？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Wait, wait... He wanted to short housing bonds?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.07,0:28:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,賭房價跌嗎？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Who bets against housing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.90,0:28:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 資產擔保證券指數到幾點了？- 這指數什麼意思？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}- What's the ABX at? - What's ABX?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.51,0:28:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 用來跟蹤次級房貸證券的價值 - 快睡你的覺！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}-It tracks sub-prime mortgage bond value. -Go back to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.75,0:28:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,指數在…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}The ABX is at ... eh....
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.52,0:28:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天！降下來了，去年到現在降了3點 這不對勁\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Wow! it's down, It's down 3 points since last year, that's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.23,0:28:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼一點動靜都沒聽到過\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I haven't heard a peep about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.96,0:28:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,這人叫啥？傑瑞德…威內特\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}What was this guys name? Jared Vennett... Vennett
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.65,0:28:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,這是真的！這群中獎了的雜種因為我撥錯的電話\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}That's right! These lucky sons of bitches caught wind
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.30,0:28:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住了華爾街歷史上最好的一樁交易\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}of one of the best trades in Wall-street history from a wrong number.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.14,0:28:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他們應該給我的錯誤電話線路抽成10%\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}They should've paid 10 percent to my fuck up state system
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.91,0:28:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,叫傑瑞德·威內特\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}He was Jared Vennett, Vennett
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.95,0:28:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 傑瑞德·威內特，德意志銀行，聽著就不靠譜 - 聽他說話就讓人不爽\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Jared Vennett, from Deutsche, sounded very sketchy. -Sounds like a douche-bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.42,0:29:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你們好啊 - 請坐\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}OK.. Hi.... how are you?! -Have a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.69,0:29:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,來自德意志銀行的傑瑞德，我們洗耳恭聽了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Hey mister Vennett from Deutsche Bank, who do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.72,0:29:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你和多少人聊過？ - 有幾個\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}So, how many people have you talked to about this trade? - A few.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.53,0:29:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有意向的還不少\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}There's definitely some interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.15,0:29:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Ohh..
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.59,0:29:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我老闆知道了非得弄死我不可\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}My boss would have my ass
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.12,0:29:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你瘋了吧？傑瑞\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}are you crazy Jer?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.12,0:29:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,別廢話！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.70,0:29:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,滾蛋！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.43,0:29:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你才打錯電話給我們\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Which is why you're here talking to us on the wrong number?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.24,0:29:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 聽著確實感興趣的人不少哇 - 好吧\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Sounds like there's a lot of interest. -Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.15,0:29:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有的人和我聊天就是看笑話尋開心 你們也不想談正事嗎？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}A few people have us in, just to laugh at me on this deal, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.88,0:29:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你們也是這意思？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Is that what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.88,0:29:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我們不是這類人，就馬克愛開這種玩笑\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}That's not what this is, that's just how Mark is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.85,0:29:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,和我們詳細說說\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Let's see what you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.82,0:29:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你聞到什麼東西了嗎？- 什麼？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I'm sorry, do you smell that, what is that? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.42,0:29:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 這是什麼味道？ - 古龍水嗎？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}What's that smell? -Cologne?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.11,0:29:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}No....
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.18,0:29:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,發財的機會！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.78,0:29:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不…錢的味道\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}No... Money.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.90,0:29:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我聞到錢味兒了…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I smell money...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.40,0:29:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Chris....
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.72,0:30:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 手腳利索點 - 抱歉\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}goddammit! -I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.32,0:30:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是你們房貸證券的構成\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}This is your basic mortgage bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.58,0:30:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,開始很簡單\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Alright, the originals were simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.94,0:30:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就是幾千個3A級房貸組合起來\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}They were just thousands of AAA-mortgages bundled together,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.72,0:30:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,政府擔保\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}guaranteed by the US-government.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.68,0:30:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,而現代的房貸證券就不一樣了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}The modern ones are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.44,0:30:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是私營的，而且由分層份額構成\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}They're private. And they're made up of layers of tranches.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.19,0:30:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,* 份額一詞來源於法語，意為某物的一部分\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*A tranche is a French word meaning "a portion of sth."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.91,0:30:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,最高的3A級最先償還\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Highest level AAA's getting paid first.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.29,0:30:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,最差的B級最後還，會首先斷供\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}The lowest rated B's getting paid last, taking on defaults first.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.58,0:30:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,顯然斷供的B級，能要回更多的錢來\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}No obviously if you're buying B's you could make more money.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.40,0:30:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是有點風險，有時候也可能償還不了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}But, they're a little risky, sometimes they fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.18,0:30:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Chris...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.14,0:30:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,某處開始，有些B級或者2B級 從有點風險，變成狗屎貸\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Somewhere along the line, these B's and BB's went from a little risky to dogshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.06,0:30:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,垃圾桶在哪\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Where's the trash?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.99,0:30:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我說的是最低的信用評分\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I'm talking rock-bottom Fico-scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.87,0:30:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有收入核實\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}No Income-verification.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.81,0:30:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可調利率貸款…就是狗屎\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}adjustable rates... Dogshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.94,0:31:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,違約率已經到了1至4個百分點\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}The default-rates are already up from one to four percent fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.88,0:31:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等到了8%…也肯定會到的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And if they rise to eight percent... and they will!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.16,0:31:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那這些3B級的房貸也會一錢不值\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}A lot of these BBB's are going to zero too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.16,0:31:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這…別離我這麼近\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And that.... You're too close...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.56,0:31:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是發財機會\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Is an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.19,0:31:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你說8%的警戒線，現在已經到4%了？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}OK, You're saying that at 8 percent the bonds fail and we're already at 4 percent?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.28,0:31:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 沒錯 - 到了8就是世界末日了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}That's right. -If they go to eight.... It's Armageddon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.29,0:31:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 那怎麼沒人提到過這事兒\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Yeah that's right. -How come nobody's talking about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.07,0:31:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你計算沒問題嗎？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And you're completely sure of the math?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.12,0:31:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看看他…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Look at him...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.99,0:31:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我的礦工！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}That's my Quant!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.33,0:31:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你的啥？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}-Your what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.40,0:31:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我的量化研究員…我的數學專家！瞧瞧他！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}My quantitative... My maths specialist! Look at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.62,0:31:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,看到有什麼與眾不同的嗎？看看他的臉！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You notice anything different about him? Look at his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.43,0:31:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你這也太種族歧視了…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}That's very racist
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.14,0:31:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,看看他的眼睛！我提示你們一下…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Look at his eyes! I'll give you a hint..
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.69,0:31:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他的名字叫做“楊”！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}His name is Yang!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.66,0:31:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他得了國家數學競賽的金牌…還是中國的競賽！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}He won a national maths competition.. In China!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.92,0:31:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,他連英語都不會說！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}He doesn't even speak English!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.65,0:31:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,所以沒錯！我對數字有信心\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Yeah! I'm sure of the math.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.03,0:31:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,其實我名字叫“江”\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Actually, my name is JIANG
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.86,0:31:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我也會說英語\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}and... I do speak English
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.85,0:32:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,傑瑞德喜歡這麼說，是想要讓我看起來更牛逼一些\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Jared likes to say it though.. because he thinks it makes me seem more authentic
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.42,0:32:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我…其實得了數學競賽第二名\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And... i got second in that national math competition
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.72,0:32:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你讓我們做空這堆積木嗎？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}So.... You're offering us a chance to short this pile of blocks?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.06,0:32:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼做空？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.51,0:32:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,用信用違約互換來做\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}With something called a credit default swap.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.04,0:32:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就像是證券的保險，不過如果證券完了 那你能拿到10倍的賠償\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}It's like insurance on the bond, and if it goes bust, you can make 10-to-1.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.20,0:32:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至有可能拿到20倍，崩潰趨勢已經開始了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Even 20-to-1 return, and it's already slowly going bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.95,0:32:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,10倍，20倍，怎麼可能！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}10-to-1, 20-to-1.... No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.49,0:32:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒人注意到\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And no-one is paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.23,0:32:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人親自去了解\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}No-one is paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.79,0:32:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,銀行忙著賣證券，暗地裡拿提成\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Because the banks are too busy getting paid obscene fees to sell these bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.40,0:32:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等…可你就是銀行的人\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}But wait.... You are the bank
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.94,0:32:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你為銀行工作，那你的提成也富的流油吧\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You work for the bank, i bet your margins are pretty nice and fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.25,0:32:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我的提成和這個沒關係\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Let's not talk about my margins by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.84,0:32:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我私事…好比我看你襯衫不錯 問你在哪買來的女裝，好玩嗎\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Being nice and fat.... That's a nice shirt, do they make it for men?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.35,0:32:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你不替銀行說話？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Aren't you the bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.34,0:32:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我給銀行打工\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I work for the bank!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.96,0:32:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我腦子沒賣給銀行\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I don't think like a bank
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.29,0:32:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,大銀行小銀行，我賺的是錢\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Big banks, small bank... I like to make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.70,0:32:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧…讓我直說\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Alright...Let me put it this way....
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.33,0:32:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這就像我來到失火大樓前面\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I'm standing in front of a burning house,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.13,0:32:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,現場讓你們買火災保險\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And I'm offering you fire insurance on it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.00,0:32:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能這些證券像你說得那麼差\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}-How can these underlying bonds be... as bad as you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.63,0:33:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人管嗎\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}It wouldn't be legal!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.84,0:33:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人知道裡面裝的什麼東西\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Nobody knows what's in them!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.78,0:33:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人知道在證券裡有什麼鬼\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Nobody knows, what's in the bonds,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.57,0:33:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我見到過65%達到3A評級的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I've seen some that are 65 percent AAA-rating.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.66,0:33:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,其實95%都是次級狗屎\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}That i know, for a fact, are filled with 95 percent sub-prime shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.23,0:33:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,信用評分都低於550 （FICO評分300-850，700以上認為是優）\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}With Fico's below 550
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.03,0:33:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你就吹吧！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Get the fuck out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.20,0:33:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真想被我吹暈了嗎？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Want me to really blow your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.49,0:33:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要是市場覺得一個證券風險太高了怎麼辦？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}When the market deems a bond too risky to buy, what do you think we do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.40,0:33:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你們猜吧！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Take a guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.82,0:33:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道，才讓你說\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I don't know, you tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.34,0:33:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.28,0:33:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你以為像書本上說的用倉單存貨抵押嗎？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You think we just warehouse it on the books?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.65,0:33:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,假的，實際上我們重新打包 混上其他賣不出去的東西\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}No, we just repackage it, with a bunch of other shit that didn't sell
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.92,0:33:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,放到CDO裡面賣\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}and put it into a CDO.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.87,0:33:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- CDO？ - 對，這東西叫CDO\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}A CDO? -Yes... a CDO.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.55,0:33:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是什麼？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.70,0:33:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,把一些沒人買的B，2B，3B級爛貸\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Where we take a bunch of B's, BB's and BBB's that haven't sold
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.98,0:33:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,打包成一堆…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}and we put em in a pile...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.25,0:33:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,數量差不多了，就忽然叫做“分散化投資”了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}and when the pile gets large enough, the whole is suddenly considered 'Diversified'.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.91,0:33:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等著…評級機構的婊子們\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}and then... the whores of the rating agency,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.96,0:33:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,評個百分之92到93的3A級別 其他屁都不放\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Give it a 92 / 93 percent AAA-rating, no questions asked...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.11,0:33:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你再說一遍！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Holy... what! Say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.29,0:33:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,CDO，擔保債務憑證\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}(CDO)Collateralized Debt Obligations
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.55,0:34:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,理解CDO很重要，CDO才是讓房產危機…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}It's important to understand, because it's what allowed the housing crisis
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.19,0:34:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,…禍害全國經濟的關鍵\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}become a nationwide economic disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.49,0:34:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我們的世界頂級廚師安東尼·伯爾頓解釋一下\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Here's world-famous chef Anthony Bourdain to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.16,0:34:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,假設我正給一個周日下午的大餐廳備菜\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}OK, I'm a chef on a Sunday-afternoon setting the menu of a big restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.93,0:34:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我周五定購的魚，就好比麥克做空的房貸證券\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I ordered my fish on Friday, which is the mortgage bond that Michael Burry shorted.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.44,0:34:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有些魚…沒賣出去…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}But... some of the fresh doesn't sell..
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.43,0:34:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道原因，沒準這比目魚成精了…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I don't know why, maybe it just came halibut
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.20,0:34:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,有海豚一樣的智商\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}has the intelligence of a dolphin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.87,0:34:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那我該怎麼辦呢？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}So... what am i gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.62,0:34:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,把這些3B評級的魚扔掉嗎？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}throw all this unsold fish, which is the BBB-level of bond, in the garbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.09,0:34:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,認虧了？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}and take the loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.84,0:34:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,沒必要！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.86,0:34:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我這麼心靈手巧…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Being a crafty and morally honorous chef that i am...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.35,0:34:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,每種賣不掉的爛證券，我都扔到海鮮湯裡去\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Every crappy levels of the bond i don't sell... i throw into a seafood stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.11,0:34:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這不再是爛魚！這是新東西！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}It's not old fish! It's a whole new thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.76,0:34:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,最妙的地方就在於…賣給顧客的名頭，是零售比目魚\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}The best part is.... They're eating retailed halibut!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.38,0:34:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這…就是CDO\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}That... is a CDO.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.29,0:34:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能這些東西被攢到一起\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I just need to know how these could possibly be correlated.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.52,0:35:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像《愛探險的朵拉》主人公 老是第一個發現大新聞\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You're like D- D- Dora the Explorering, you're the first person who has found this...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.82,0:35:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等…你是說房貸證券是狗屎？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}So.. hold on.. So mortgage bonds are dogshit?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.37,0:35:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,CDO是貓屎包起來的狗屎\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}CDO's are dogshit wrapped in catshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.88,0:35:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,對，就是這個理兒\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Yeah... that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.86,0:35:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,機構們還把CDO當成國庫券一樣的寶貝\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Institutions treat these CDO's like they're as solid as treasury bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.44,0:35:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,等著它們一錢不值吧\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}and they're going to zero..
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.84,0:35:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不對啊，去年一年就賣了5千億的房貸證券\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}No, that can't be right, there, there, are 500 billion in housing bonds sold last year alone
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.15,0:35:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,信用評級機構，銀行 政府也摻和在裡面？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Ratings agencies, the banks.... the fucking government?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.62,0:35:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你這就像在說他們閉著眼開車\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You're saying they're all asleep at the wheel?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.68,0:35:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯！我整個部門都對這種狗屎流口水\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Yeah! My whole department is long this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.94,0:35:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他們反倒叫我膽小雞仔\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}They call me chicken little.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.63,0:35:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他們叫我泡沫男孩\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}They call me Bubble-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.53,0:35:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,A級…廢了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}A's ... Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.70,0:35:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,B級廢了，2B級廢了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}B's.. Zero, BB's ..... Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.97,0:35:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,3B級…也是廢品\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}BBB's .... Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.97,0:35:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來就是這個了！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And then that happens!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.42,0:35:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這…是啥？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}What... is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.00,0:35:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是美國的房產市場\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}That's America's housing market.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.90,0:35:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 謝謝 - 你說得好棒！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Thank you. - Fucking A Jared!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.88,0:35:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,給我閉嘴！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Shut your fucking mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.99,0:36:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,再見 傑瑞德！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Bye Jared!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.60,0:36:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這不對勁\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I don't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.19,0:36:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定有貓膩\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}He's playing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.72,0:36:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他在玩我們，他陷得太深了，拉人墊背來脫身\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}He's playing us, he's got too much skin in the game, and he's dumping his position.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.35,0:36:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他說的是真的呢\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}What if he's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.07,0:36:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你當然希望他說的是真的！ - 我是希望！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You want him to be right! -Yes, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.03,0:36:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,銀行給我們信用卡的利息是25%\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}The banks have given us twenty-five percent interest rates on credit cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.73,0:36:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,助學貸款也坑了大家，普通人已經沒法脫身了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}They have screwed us on student-loans, so we can never get out from under.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.79,0:36:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,然後這傢伙，走到我辦公室裡說\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Then this guy, walks into my office and says:
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.52,0:36:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這些銀行太貪婪，已經忽視了市場真相了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}"Those same banks got greedy, they lost track of the market"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.38,0:36:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,然後我還能通過他們的愚蠢賺錢\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And i can profit off of their stupidity
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.73,0:36:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我靠！我當然希望他是對的！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Fuck! Yeah! I want him to be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.73,0:36:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼能不討厭他？ 你告誡我們注意的騙子特徵他身上全有\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I mean, how come you don't hate this guy? He's everything you taught us not to trust!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.25,0:36:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨不起來！他這麼把自己的利益擺到檯面上 我倒挺尊敬他\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You can't hate him! He is so transparent in his self-interest that i kinda respect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.26,0:37:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我會從這種人手裡買車嗎？肯定不會\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Would i buy a car from him?... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.82,0:37:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他說的房貸市場情況是否屬實？ 咱們自己去調查看看，去調查\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Is he right about the mortgage market? Let's find out. Let's find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.93,0:37:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我們只要回答兩個簡單問題\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Look... It's two very simple questions:
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.07,0:37:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,房地產有沒有泡沫？如果有，銀行了解多少？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Is there a housing bubble? And if there is... how exposed are the banks?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.23,0:37:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,咱們趕快行動，如果情況屬實\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Let's get on this quickly too, because if he is right...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.14,0:37:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那有點錢的基金都會來找我們的麻煩\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Every loser with a couple million bucks in a fund is gonna be jumping on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.11,0:37:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,現在就出發！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.94,0:37:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,摩根大通啊，這裡可是摩根大通啊\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}J.P. Morgan-Chase, J.P. Morgan-Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.64,0:37:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,*查理·蓋勒 別廢話了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}* Charlie Geller OK.. Don't!...Stop Saying J.P. Morgan-Chase!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.56,0:37:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得咱們能交好運\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I got a good feeling about this
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.19,0:37:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,* 傑米·希普利 就一個會面，別抱太大期望\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}* Jamie Shipley Just a meeting though, you know...It's just a meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.97,0:37:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,會面天天都有…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}People have meetings all the time... You know!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.03,0:37:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,人們喝完咖啡，就去會面…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}People drink their coffee, they have a meeting...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.00,0:37:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- 棕地基金？ - 我們在這兒！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Brownfield Funds? - Yes!  yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.21,0:37:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫克里斯，泰德交易團隊的前台\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Hello, Hey! Chris... I 'm on Ted's Desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.53,0:37:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫查理，查理·蓋勒 我叫傑米，傑米·希普利\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I'm Charlie, I'm Charlie Geller, I'm Jamie, Jamie Shipley.. Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.19,0:38:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我們太想在你們的交易平台上接入了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}We're so excited to get setup on your trading platform!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.17,0:38:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,很好啊！先坐下聊一聊\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Cool! Here, eh.. have a seat a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.67,0:38:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.92,0:38:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我…泰德讓我…先和你們見面聊聊\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}So I... Ted did ask ehm.. to do us some meeting in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.03,0:38:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可我一直找不到你們的宣傳資料\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}but I eh... I couldn't find any marketing material on you guys..
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.41,0:38:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…我們是剛從科羅拉多州博爾德搬過來\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Oh... we just moved here from Boulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.85,0:38:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看看你們的招募書嗎？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Oh, can we see some of your offering documents?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.91,0:38:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,其實，棕地基金用的是…我們自己的錢\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Well Brownfield has it own... money...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.13,0:38:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我倆的存款…嗯\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}It's our money... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.09,0:38:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,說說你們資金規模是多大？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Well can you tell us how much you manage?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.14,0:38:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊！我們現在做到3千萬了…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Of course! We're doing 30 million right now.... eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.41,0:38:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我們是4年前開始的 當時只有11萬的本錢\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}But we started four years ago, with a hundred-ten thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.37,0:38:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 厲害啊！- 所以你看\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Wow! -So as you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.05,0:38:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的投資回報率相當厲害\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}that's pretty phenomenal returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.46,0:38:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我們想和摩根簽署ISDA協議\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}We wanna get an ISDA-agreement with J.P. Morgan,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.03,0:38:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣我們就能交易長線期權了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}So we can deal in long-term options.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.44,0:38:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 想法很好嘛！- 是啊\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}-That's really cool! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.56,0:38:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,*ISDA協議（國際掉期及衍生產品協議）\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*ISDA Agreement
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.86,0:38:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,*這個協議能夠讓投資者坐在“大亨”席位上\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*An agreement that lets an investor sit at the "big boy table"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.86,0:38:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,*阻止愚蠢的新手擾亂高水平的交易\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*and make high level trades not available to stupid amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.20,0:38:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,*押注很大的交易員，如果沒有ISDA\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*Trying to be a high stakes trader without an ISDA
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.40,0:38:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,*就像騎著羊駝，想要贏得超級印地賽車比賽冠軍一樣\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*is like trying to win the Indy 500 riding a llama.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.41,0:38:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你們的想法很好！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}That is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.46,0:39:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.53,0:39:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不過呢…你們沒達到ISDA的資本準入門檻\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}But eh.. you guys are under the capital requirements for an ISDA.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.29,0:39:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,差多少？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}By how much?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.77,0:39:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…差了…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Er.. How much eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.15,0:39:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,十億四千七百萬\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}One billion four-hundred-seventy millions
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.72,0:39:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.08,0:39:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,還差挺多\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}A lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.12,0:39:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這讓我們看起來挺不專業的，是嗎\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}This makes us look bad doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.57,0:39:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我們連資金要求都不知道\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}That we didn't know what the capital requirements were.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.68,0:39:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I..... eh..
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.24,0:39:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,影響是不太積極\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}It's not great!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.28,0:39:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不過呢\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}But, eh.....
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.40,0:39:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你們保持這樣的利潤率\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Keep up those returns
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.89,0:39:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,以後發達了，記得再給我們打電話\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And give us a call way down the line you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.11,0:39:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好嗎？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.93,0:39:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，謝謝你克里斯！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}OK, of course! Thanks Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.70,0:39:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 祝你們好運！- 謝謝！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Have a good one guys! -Thank you Chris!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.47,0:39:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.25,0:39:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,誰會安排下午4點50談正事兒\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Who the fuck schedules a meeting at 4:50 in the afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.54,0:39:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,美國銀行和貝爾斯登沒回電話也就算了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Dude, B of A and Bear didn't even return our calls
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.12,0:39:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- 連美聯銀行這種大眾貨也不屌我們！ - 是啊\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}and even fucking Wachovia blew us off! - I know man!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.01,0:39:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這是其他一樣在大廳裡就被拍死的傢伙的招股書\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Here's the prospectuses of all the other losers who didn't make it past the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.64,0:39:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不想搞這個了…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I don't think i can do this anymore..
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.95,0:40:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,夥計，我還年輕，還能幹點正事兒！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Yo, I'm young yet, i can still do something with my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.09,0:40:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我想回科羅拉多老家 連大麻都比這邊的飄\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I miss Colorado anyway. The weed's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.09,0:40:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,先生們…請離開大廳\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Gentleman... i need you to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.44,0:40:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好，我們馬上走，咱們走\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Yep, Yeah we're going, Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.94,0:40:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,看這個！看看這個！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Look at this, Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.85,0:40:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,這人說房地產市場就是一個大泡沫！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}this guy says that the housing market is a giant bubble!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.92,0:40:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這部分情節和真實情況有些出入\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}OK, so this part isn't totally accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.25,0:40:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我倆不是在大廳發現了傑瑞德的推銷資料\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Now, we didn't find Jared Vennett's housing bubble pitch in a lobby of a bank that rejected us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.56,0:40:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,實際情況是，一個朋友告訴了查理這件事\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Truth is... ehm.. A friend had told Charlie about it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.05,0:40:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是從金融史學家Jim Grant的個人期刊上讀到的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And I read about it, in Grant?ˉs Interest Rate Observer
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.36,0:40:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢相信！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.83,0:40:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,簡直像胡說的東西\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}This is..... crazy stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.86,0:40:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這兒說房貸證券的信用違約互換\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Here, they're saying that there's 10-to-1 returns,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.20,0:40:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是10倍的收益比\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}on Credit Default Swaps for mortgage backed securities
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.93,0:40:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,現在房地產市場馬上就要崩潰了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}and the whole housing market is about to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.11,0:40:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,對他倆來說，聽到這消息簡直像貓聞到了腥味一樣\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}For Jamie and Charlie, the housing market doomsday prediction was music to their ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.97,0:40:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,bgm 《Lithium》by Polyphonic Spree\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*bgm:  Lithium by Polyphonic Spree
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.03,0:40:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他倆在傑米家的車庫創業起家\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}They had started working out of Jamie's garage,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.48,0:41:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,資金是傑米在東海岸倒賣帆船攢下來的11萬\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}with a 110 thousand Jamie had saved taking sailboats up and down the east-coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.25,0:41:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我們的投資策略很簡單\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Our investment-strategy was simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.28,0:41:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人願意聽到壞消息 所以人們往往低估壞事發生的概率\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}People hate to think about bad things happening so they always underestimate their likelihood.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.68,0:41:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,簡單又高明的策略\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Their strategy simple and brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.72,0:41:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,他說的對！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}What he said!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.91,0:41:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他倆發現，市場會低價販賣 認為不可能發生的事情的期權\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Jamie and Charlie found: Markets will sell options very cheaply on things they think will never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.90,0:41:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣損失會很小，而一旦得利…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}So, when they were wrong, they were wrong small. But when they were right.......
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.92,0:41:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就能賺很多！ -賺翻了！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}They were right big! - Boooooom!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.19,0:41:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,*期權交易的是“買賣權利”，不需要買賣實物\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*options
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.39,0:41:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,*所以需要的資金量小，可以做空\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*options
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.25,0:41:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,（棕地基金） 幾年間他們就把11萬做到了3千萬\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*BROWNFIELD FUND Within a few years they had turned a 110 grand into 30 million
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.42,0:41:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是時候去紐約了…不過進展並不順利\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Then it was time to go to New York City, And so far..... It wasn't going very well
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.56,0:41:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要是這個買賣可以做呢？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}So what if it does seem interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.13,0:41:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，沒有銀行會和我們簽ISDA協議\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Nope, no bank will give us our ISDA.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.35,0:41:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,咱們沒風掀不起浪啊…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}We're dead in the water...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.58,0:41:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這類交易完全搞不起\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}These kind of trades are totally out of the question!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.19,0:41:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,咱們必須打電話給本\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}-We gotta call Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.06,0:41:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,打給他！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Call Ben!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.27,0:41:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,本·瑞克是退下來的交易員 以前在摩根新加坡分行\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Ben Ricker was a former trader in Singapore for Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.27,0:41:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,深深厭惡這一行就金盆洗手了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Quit the whole game in disgust!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.22,0:42:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,當年在科羅拉多州，本正好是傑米的鄰居\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}He just happened to be Jamie's neighbor when they were in Colorado
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.93,0:42:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,因為本在遛狗，兩人才認識\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}They met, walking dogs....
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.92,0:42:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不過本的世界觀更陰暗\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}But Ben was dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.49,0:42:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不只認為金融系統會崩潰\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}He didn't just think the whole system would fail
