Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.24,0:48:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,也就你這麼想！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Says you!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.28,0:48:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,在合約到期前，基金裡有多少錢可以撤回？ 就算半年之內吧\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}How much is eligible for withdrawal before they're due? Say in the next two quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.34,0:48:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你的投資人恐慌了的話\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}If your investors panic
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.08,0:48:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,3億零2百萬\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}302
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.94,0:48:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙啊，麥克\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}My god Mike!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.32,0:48:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不會有人往外取錢的，那樣損人不利己\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}No-one will pull out, that would be suicide man
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.10,0:48:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,今年雖然下跌了17%，但相信我就行了 而且他們一直相信我\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Down 17 percent for the year, but if they trust me, and they trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.18,0:48:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人相信你！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}No-one trusts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.96,0:48:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 沒人！ - 我寫了幾封信給投資人了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}No-one! -I've sent several e-mails to my investors
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.98,0:48:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他們了解情況\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Letting them know that the.. the....
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.48,0:48:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,07年的第二季度，我們房貸投資就能盈利\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}It's the second quarter of '07 is when our housing position shows returns
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.00,0:48:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我說得很清楚了！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}and ehm... I've been very clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.78,0:48:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你就等著大家撤資吧\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}People will withdraw their money!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.02,0:48:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,為啥？誰會這麼傻？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Why? You'd have to be so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.72,0:49:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我們基金的資本減少過多\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}If, if  if the funds capital drops too much....
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.44,0:49:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼互換合同就會自動失效\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}then the swaps contracts are voided
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.84,0:49:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,然後銀行…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}and then the banks....
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.10,0:49:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就會拿走所有錢，一個子兒都不剩\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}get to keep all of it, all of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.26,0:49:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,合同會自動失效？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}The contracts are voided?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.50,0:49:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,合同會自動失效？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}The contracts are voided!?!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.34,0:49:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我去！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.32,0:49:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你這臭不要臉的！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}O, motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.84,0:49:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,麥克\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Michael....
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.78,0:49:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,把我的錢還我\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Give me my money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.90,0:49:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,麥克，聽見了嗎？我要退回我的錢！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Michael, do you hear me? I want my money back!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.86,0:49:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你把我的錢給我！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Give me my fucking money back!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.20,0:49:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你這小兔崽子\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You motherfucker!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.50,0:49:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,房產市場正處在一個小不丁點的低谷裡\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}The market is in an itsy-bitsy little gully right now
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.98,0:49:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好像大夥說“玩得太嗨了，咱們稍微緩緩神”\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Like everybody said: "OK, that was crazy, let's just all calm down!"
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.86,0:49:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那房子剛建成的時候，我35萬賣了出去\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I sold that house for 350, the year it was built.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.62,0:49:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,兩年以後，就值48萬，然後58萬5 這是一年半以前的價格\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}two years later... 480, then 585, maybe eighteen months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.20,0:49:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這對夫妻在去年花65萬買了下來\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}This couple bought it for 650 last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.56,0:50:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,倒霉碰上房價跌了，只能按原價賣唄\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}He'd let it go for that....high jump
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.40,0:50:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,他肯定覺得不值，不過會放手的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}It will break his heart, but he'll let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.28,0:50:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那他為什麼要賣房？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Why is he selling?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.96,0:50:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,夫妻倆現在都沒工作\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Neither one is working right now
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.80,0:50:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,馬琳，你說他們急於出手是吧？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Marlene, you'd say they're motivated, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.70,0:50:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,和這片的人積極性差不多吧\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}As motivated as one can be in this neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.82,0:50:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,左邊這房子，才是真正急於出手\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}This house on the left, I'd say they're properly motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.60,0:50:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我說，急於出手的也太多了點\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Wow! A lot of people seem very motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.66,0:50:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,房價小觸底嘛，大夥神經過敏\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}It's just a gully that's all. Just nerves
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.14,0:50:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那…我們把車停到哪兒\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}So... where do we stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.76,0:50:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我得和我老婆商量一下\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I need to talk to my wife
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.62,0:50:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,再等，過了這村就沒這店了！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}ehm.. This market won't last!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.00,0:50:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,其實，能給我介紹個房貸經紀人嗎？ 你推薦的，不錯的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Actually, can i talk to a mortgage broker? Anybody you recommend? Anybody you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.88,0:50:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有啊，是有個絕佳人選\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Yes, yes, There's someone, absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.94,0:50:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這小妞肯定喜歡我啊 我幫她賺錢賺翻了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Yeah, bitch better like me, sent her ass to Cabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.06,0:50:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,連摩根士丹利都等著要我們了？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}So is Morgan Stanley recruiting us? Is that..
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.18,0:50:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,不是…銀行擁有我們的對沖基金\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}No, eh no. The bank owns our hedge-fund
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.10,0:50:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們其實不歸銀行管 我們主要投資金融服務公司\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}We're not really a part of it, we invest in financial service companies.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.98,0:50:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我們過來是想了解這裡房貸行業的情況\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}We're trying to understand the residential mortgage business.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.66,0:50:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你每個月能辦多少筆貸款\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}How many loans do you write each month?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.66,0:51:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒留意過，大概60筆吧\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I don't know, about 60.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.24,0:51:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,4年前呢？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}What was it four years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.82,0:51:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,10筆…15筆的樣子\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Ten.... but maybe fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.60,0:51:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,以前我是酒吧招待，現在我連船都有了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I was a bartender, now i own a boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.80,0:51:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡面有多少是可調利率的房貸？ （*前幾年低利率，然後調高）\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}So, how many of these are eh.. adjustable rate mortgages?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.18,0:51:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，絕大多數\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Well, most.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.08,0:51:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是，我覺得有90%左右\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Yeah, I'd say about ninety percent
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.26,0:51:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,近幾年這種房貸提成飆上天了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}The bonuses on those skyrocketed a few years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.32,0:51:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我們全靠這個賺錢\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Adjustables are bread and honey
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.76,0:51:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那房貸申請有被拒的時候嗎\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}So, do applicants ever get rejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.52,0:51:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.52,0:51:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他們被拒，我就不稱職了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Look if they get rejected I suck at my job!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.50,0:51:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他們沒錢也能貸到款？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Even if they have no money?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.36,0:51:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我們公司有一種“忍者貸款”\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Well, my firm offers a NINJA loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.52,0:51:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要收入和職業證明，收入一欄空著都可以\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}No Income No Job Application, I just leave the income-section blank if i want.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.44,0:51:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,公司不在乎\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Corporate doesn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.76,0:51:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 大夥想要房，公司順應民意唄 - 你當然願意\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}- These people just want homes, and they go with the flow. - Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.78,0:51:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你們公司都不查驗的嗎\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Your companies don't verify?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.02,0:51:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我星期五下午簽了房貸合同\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}If I write a loan on Friday afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.88,0:51:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大銀行周一中午就會買走\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Big bank is gonna buy it by Monday lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.26,0:51:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,見怪不怪！我們也一樣\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Deal! Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.44,0:52:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你們能等會嗎？ - 行啊\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Could you hold on a second? -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.88,0:52:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我搞不明白，為啥他們這麼坦白\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I don't get it... Why are they confessing?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.74,0:52:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他們不是在坦白…他們這是在吹牛\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}They're not confessing.... They're bragging!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.30,0:52:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,貸款的人真的知道這種貸款的風險嗎？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Do people have any idea what they are buying?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.10,0:52:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我一般找移民\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I focus on immigrants!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.46,0:52:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,等他們還不起房貸睡大街了… 你讓他們簽什麼都願意\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Once they find out they're getting homeless.. They'll sign where you tell em to sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.82,0:52:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不會問問題，不理解利率是什麼東西\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}They don't ask questions, don't understand the rates.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.60,0:52:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你也找移民下手嗎？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And you targeting on immigrants too?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.60,0:52:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,移民的信用分對他來說還太好\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Their credit isn't actually bad enough for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.70,0:52:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不跟錢過不去\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Look I'm a yield guy
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.20,0:52:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一筆固定利率的良性房貸，我只賺兩千\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I make two thousand on a fixed rate prime
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.72,0:52:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可做一筆可調利率的次級貸，我能賺一萬\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}But i CAN make ten thousand on a sub-prime adjustable
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.38,0:52:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,說真的，沒有脫衣舞女郎的幫忙 我也開不上寶馬7系\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Trust me, I'm not driving that 7-series without strippers
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.42,0:53:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,她們信用評分都不行，可是都超級有錢\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}No-one on the pole has good credit, and they're all cash-rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.60,0:53:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像聽沃倫·巴菲特說過類似的話\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I think I read Warren Buffett said something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.80,0:53:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？巴菲特是誰？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}What? Who's Warren Buffett?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.38,0:53:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你說的脫衣舞女郎…就是露肉的那種？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}OK, So, strippers.... like exotic dancers...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.46,0:53:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,光屁股的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Nude, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.76,0:53:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,露著胸的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Topless..
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.50,0:53:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 脫衣舞女郎 - 對\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Strippers? -Yeah, Hmmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.02,0:53:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能幫我們介紹個嗎？ - 當然行\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Can you introduce us? Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.50,0:53:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.74,0:53:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直選還貸方式多的可調房貸 我畢竟是自由職業者\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I always get option-pay adjustable. I'm a private contractor.
