Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.72,1:09:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,閉嘴！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.28,1:09:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他們腳都開始著火了，心裡卻想著牛排應該烤熟了 你還覺得奇怪？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}now their foot's on fire and they think their steak is done, and you're surprised?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.40,1:09:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是愚蠢，這是詐騙\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}That's not stupidity... that's fraud!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.28,1:09:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟我說清楚愚蠢和違法的區別 我就去把我小舅子抓起來\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Tell me the difference between stupid and illegal and I'll have my wife's brother arrested.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.12,1:09:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 挺好笑的！ - 你們還是沒弄明白整個系統有多蠢\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}That was funny! -I guess you just don't realize how clueless the system really is!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.64,1:09:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我承認，是有一些見不得人的勾當\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Yes, there's some shady shit going down!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.02,1:09:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但相信我，這是愚蠢驅使的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}but trust me, it's fueled by stupidity!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.80,1:09:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你們這些人\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Look at yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.72,1:09:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,都覺得自己是敢於懷疑的人\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You know you passed yourselves off as cynical people but....
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.32,1:10:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,可你們還對這幫青天大老爺抱有希望？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You still have some faith in the system don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.82,1:10:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不抱\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I don't
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.06,1:10:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,文尼是明白人！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Well, except for Vinnie!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.10,1:10:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,誰在乎？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Who gives a shit?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.98,1:10:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不行！- 聽我說\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}No way! -Look!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.98,1:10:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要麼我們對，要麼我們錯得離譜\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Either we're right, or we're wrong in a giant, giant way!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.32,1:10:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真錯了，得找高人給我們點醒才行\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And if we're wrong then we gotta find someone to help us get out of this trade
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.98,1:10:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在是一點都不覺得我們占理\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I'm not feeling remotely confident that we're right
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.50,1:10:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,萬一咱們錯了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And, and... If we're wrong
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.06,1:10:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,誰來告訴我們？有誰懂？沒人懂！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Who's gonna tell us? Who understands this stuff? It makes no sense!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.06,1:10:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我們應該去拉斯維加斯！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I think we need to go to Vegas!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.86,1:10:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那兒有什麼？ - 去哪兒幹啥\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}What's in Vegas? -Vegas!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.20,1:10:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,拉斯維加斯又能有什麼東西？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}What the hell is in Las Vegas?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.20,1:10:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,下周那裡召開美國證券化論壇年會\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}The American Securitization Forum is there next week
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.52,1:10:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,每個證券、CDO、次級貸、倒賣交換的交易員都會去\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Every bond and CDO-salesman, sub-prime lender and swap-trader is gonna be there
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.22,1:10:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我這麼說\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I'm telling you
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.40,1:10:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你掙的是他們手裡的錢\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Your bet is against their money,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.98,1:10:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是時候去看看人傻錢多是怎麼回事了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}it's about time you find out just how dumb that money really is
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.90,1:10:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我真不喜歡拉斯維加斯\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}God no, I hate Vegas!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.14,1:10:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說吃的東西特別好，那裡也有松久壽司店了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I hear the food has gotten really good in Vegas, they have a Nobu now
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.86,1:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不惦記著吃嗎\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}could you fucking stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.04,1:10:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,*美國證券化論壇，拉斯維加斯\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*American Securitization Forum, Las Vegas
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.24,1:11:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,bgm:《The Phantom of the Opera》by Andrew Webber\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*bgm: THE Phantom of the Opera, by Andrew Lloyd Webber
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.24,1:11:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,*汽車抵押貸款 工資日貸款\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*Auto Title Loans & Payday Loans
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.04,1:11:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,*凱撒宮酒店\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}* Caesars Palace
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.04,1:11:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,*擇一抵押公司CEO保羅·丹頓\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}* Option One CEO Paul Dantone
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.34,1:11:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,*房貸市場仍然穩健，後勁十足\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}* The Mortgage Market is Strong & Getting Stronger
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.02,1:11:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,證券“貴”的意思是？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}... in a sense? -If the bond is "rich", it is...?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.28,1:11:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只說明證券定價過高\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}that just means it's overpriced
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.28,1:11:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 飛機上睡不著我就自己準備了一下 - 咱們集中精神！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I can't sleep on a plane so I did my homework -OK, let's focus!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.58,1:11:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是為了什麼來的？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}What's our goal?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.20,1:11:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,搞清楚這買賣是千載難逢的機會\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Figure out if this is a deal of a lifetime or...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.68,1:11:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,還是別人比我們懂得都多 咱們回頭會虧大發了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}everyone knows here something we don't and we're gonna get royally screwed
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.20,1:11:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,和貝爾公司的人接觸的時候 注意你們的目的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Right, remember that when you meet with guys from Bear!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.12,1:12:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我給你們安排見面機會\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I'll set you up with a face-to-face
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.92,1:12:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，地方在哪？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Awesome, where is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.36,1:12:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天！5年前這年會還是窮鬼聚會\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Holy shit! Five years ago Securitization was a loser-convention
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.88,1:12:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,也就有100到200人出席\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}a hundred, maybe two-hundred people would show
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.08,1:12:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,產業每年五千億的發展之後，就變成這樣了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}500 billion dollars a year later you get this!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.10,1:12:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡自帶裝逼表情的人還真多\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}There's a lot of smug-looking people in here huh!?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.78,1:12:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好像暴發戶白人都跑來了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}It looks like someone just hit a pinata that was filled with white people who suck at golf
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.68,1:12:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 都從哪兒冒出來的？ - 別抱怨了，肯定很好玩\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I mean, who are all these clown? -Ah come on, I think it looks fun!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.44,1:12:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,查理，傑瑞德說咱們賺的是這些人的錢\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Charlie, Vennett says these are the people we're betting against.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.02,1:12:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,咱們過去，克里斯，到我左邊去，別擋道\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Yeah, here we go Chris on my left, Chris, on my left!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.64,1:12:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 大家好 - 什麼時候能見到你說的那些愛心天使\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Gentlemen! -When do we get a chance to face-time with some of these lovely folks?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.04,1:12:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯，把門卡發給他們\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Chris, give em the key cards!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.60,1:12:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,別弄混了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Do you even know which key-cords you're giving out?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.00,1:12:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 先生們路上還順利嗎？ - 沒什麼事兒\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}First of all, how was your travel? -Uneventful?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.84,1:12:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 沒事 - 我來了6小時了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Uneventful! -OK, I've been here for six hours!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.26,1:12:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經鍛煉完，吃了兩個荷包蛋 還和演員斯坦頓一起打牌\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I've already been to the Gym, I had two poached eggs, and I played blackjack with Harry Dean Stanton
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.10,1:12:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你記日記還真清楚\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Thank you for your diary!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.94,1:12:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想找人見面聊 - 提醒你們記住，我們是來收集信息的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Face-time! I'd like some face-time! -Just remember, we're here just to gather information!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.14,1:12:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是收集信息，不要打草驚蛇\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}We're gathering information, we're not advertising our short-position!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.78,1:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,別嚇到大夥兒，行不行？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Right? We don't want to spook anybody! Can we do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.96,1:12:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你說話太直，還老是不停嘴\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You got a big mouth, and you like to run it
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.48,1:13:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 這幾天能不能收斂一點？ - 好吧，好吧\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Can you just keep it shut for a few days? -OK, OK!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.38,1:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心，我們會好好套話的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Yeah, don't worry, we'll play nice!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.18,1:13:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,女士們先生們\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.92,1:13:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,商業形勢大好\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Business is good!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.20,1:13:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,利潤也很高！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Profits are strong!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.58,1:13:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,房貸還堅持著經濟的中流砥柱作用\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}and the mortgage continues to be the bedrock on which this economy is built.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.74,1:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,去年我們在次級貸市場有些損失\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Yes, we had to take some losses in our sub-prime department last year,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.48,1:13:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不過預計也就最多損失5%\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}But those losses, will be contained at only five percent!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.40,1:13:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來說\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Now
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.38,1:13:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我們住宅業務板塊的表現\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}In our residential sector...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.96,1:13:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,馬克，這不是提問環節！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Mark, it's not a Q&A!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:29.02,1:13:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我們推出的可調利率房貸被一搶而空\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}our roll out of those variable rate-packages were gobbled up by the
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.52,1:13:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我有個問題！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I have a question please!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.58,1:13:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,先生，本來提問環節是在我陳述之後 但看你這麼著急\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Sir, the Q&A is after my statement, but you know what, you seem anxious!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.68,1:13:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 現在就問吧，你好啊 - 你好，謝謝！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}How can I help you? -How are you? Fine, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.20,1:13:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Would you say,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.40,1:13:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,有沒有這個可能性，或者說必然性\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}that is it a possibility, or a probability
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.88,1:13:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,次級貸的損失最多升到5%封頂？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}that sub-prime losses stop at five percent?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.54,1:13:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.48,1:13:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得這簡直是必然的，是的！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I would say it is a very strong probability, indeed!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.80,1:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,再回到住宅部分\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}So, ehm, back to the residential sector,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.50,1:14:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我們推出可調利率… - 我還沒問完\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}when we rolled out the new variable rates package -Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.16,1:14:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這位先生\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}The ehm. Yes Sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.64,1:14:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,零！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Zero!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:08.82,1:14:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,零！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Zero!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.70,1:14:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,零！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}ZERO!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.14,1:14:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可能性為零\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}There is a zero percent chance
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.04,1:14:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,次級貸止損到5%的可能性為\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}that your sub-prime losses will stop at five percent!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.06,1:14:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,零！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Zero!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.12,1:14:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Excuse me!
