Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.80,1:44:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,摩根輸了爛賭注，卻讓我們來還賬？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Morgan makes a sucker's bet and we pay their fucking gambling debt?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.88,1:44:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 做空摩根的股票！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Short the bank's stocks! -Wait..
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.46,1:44:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,或者等市場一開始交易，就賣了我們的互換\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Or we sell our swaps, when the market opens
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.28,1:44:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我們拿到獎金，我們的投資人拿到收益\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}We get our bonuses, our investors get their profit
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.82,1:44:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,咱們能拿到一塊錢裡的三毛錢 至少能保命\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}We get... thirty cents on the dollar, Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.02,1:44:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我們比這值3倍\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}We're three times that
Dialogue: 0,1:44:23.66,1:44:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,要是買家市場都沒了，就爛到手裡了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Not if there's no market up to sell them in
Dialogue: 0,1:44:25.44,1:44:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，我不能把救生船送給這些人\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Forget it, I'm not giving any lifeboats
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.52,1:44:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,馬克，如果摩根垮了，到頭來我們什麼都沒有了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Mark, if Morgan goes under, we end up with nothing!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.94,1:44:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,文尼\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Vinnie...
Dialogue: 0,1:44:32.56,1:44:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,別爭了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Jesus, come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:34.42,1:44:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我說賣，咱們再賣\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I say, when we sell
Dialogue: 0,1:44:40.10,1:44:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你跟華爾街有私人恩怨\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Look I get that this is personal for you,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.66,1:44:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是我們對投資人也要負責 - 我們不需要負責\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}But we have a fiduciary responsibility -No, no we don't!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.70,1:44:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我們負責？這裡誰給別人負責？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Respons..? Nobody is acting responsible!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:49.04,1:44:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,責任！跟我談負責\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Fuck responsibility! Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.48,1:44:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,大銀行的那些混蛋們，回頭能…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}The assholes at the big banks, are gonna take..
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.38,1:44:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你們點菜嗎？ - 我們在說正經事…別打擾\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You boys want menu's now? -We're talking!.. Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.00,1:44:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.64,1:45:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我們要等著，耐心等著\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}We are going to wait, and we are going to wait
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.86,1:45:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,等到他們知道疼了，開始流血了才行\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}We are going to wait, until they feel the pain, until they start to bleed
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.58,1:45:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這才是我想要的結果\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}That is what I want
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.52,1:45:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們的客戶怎麼辦 我們在拿他們的錢冒風險\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Yeah, but what about our clients, they've been trusting us with their savings.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.86,1:45:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我說賣，我們再出手\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I say when we sell!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.20,1:45:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是你公報私仇的時候\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}This isn't about you!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.52,1:45:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我說賣，再出手！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Hey, hey, HEY! I say when we sell!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.78,1:45:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，那聽你的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Whatever you say Mark
Dialogue: 0,1:45:30.14,1:45:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,夥計你看新聞了嗎\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Dude, did you hear the news?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:33.82,1:45:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,兩個貝爾投資的房貸對沖基金爆倉了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Ok, so not only did two mortgage hedge-funds backed by Bear-Stearns go belly-up
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.10,1:45:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,而且現在貝爾還被集體訴訟\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}but now, there's a class-action lawsuit against Bear
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.64,1:45:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,壞了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:42.62,1:45:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我做！用力！用力！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Let's go! Push, Push!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.30,1:45:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那怎麼了？貝爾會破產嗎？ - 我們不能冒這個險\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}So? What? Bear could really collapse here? -That's a risk we really shouldn't take!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.22,1:45:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我們有80%的互換，是從貝爾那裡買的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}But eighty percent of our swaps is Bear
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.88,1:45:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我們可能陪個精光\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}We lose everything!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.14,1:45:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 先生！- 馬上就好\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Hey Sir! -One second!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.86,1:45:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- 這是我的看法 - 我們買了這東西，卻不知道怎麼賣\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}That's my opinion! -Aw, we bought these fucking things, and we have no clue how to sell them
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.54,1:45:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，所以我們得找本幫忙\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I know, we have to get Ben to do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.06,1:46:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直給他打電話，他也不回\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I've been trying to call him, but he won't get back to me
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.82,1:46:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,現在他和老婆一家人在度假，在英國！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}No, he's on vacation with his wife's family! They're in England!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.34,1:46:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.42,1:46:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,* 黑馬酒吧，英國南部港口艾克斯茅斯\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}* The Black Horse Pub, Exmouth England
Dialogue: 0,1:46:11.02,1:46:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,（本：現在出手還太早）\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}* too soon for that
Dialogue: 0,1:46:14.28,1:46:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,本，你能聽清嗎\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Hello, Ben? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.34,1:46:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你們好 - 我們在，你能聽清嗎\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Guys? -Yeah, we're here, can you hear us?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:17.56,1:46:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽的清楚\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Guys?- We hear ya, Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:20.18,1:46:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我這裡電話和網絡信號都不好\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I probably got cell-phone and WiFi-service
Dialogue: 0,1:46:23.24,1:46:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,居然要這樣賣掉2億的證券\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I'm trying to sell 200 million dollars worth of securities
Dialogue: 0,1:46:26.16,1:46:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,就在這酒吧\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}In a pub...
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.64,1:46:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,聞著綿羊味兒\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}smells like sheep
Dialogue: 0,1:46:28.92,1:46:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你能行的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You can do this!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:29.80,1:46:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想給你壓力 但你搞不定的話，我們就全賠光了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I don't want to pressure you Ben, but if you don't pull this off, we lose everything!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.08,1:46:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,看看瑞士瑞信銀行的胃口如何\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Ok, let's see what Credit Suisse's appetite is.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:42.48,1:46:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我是棕地基金，我想要拋售我的信用違約互換\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}This is Brownfield Fund, I'm wanting to unload my credit default swaps.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.00,1:46:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好的，你們有多少\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Alright, what've you got?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:47.62,1:46:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,大概有20個2A級別的CDO\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Twenty Double-A tranches of CDO's
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.92,1:46:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧…這些現在行情不太好\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Eh yes.. but these eh... these are pretty bad
Dialogue: 0,1:46:52.36,1:46:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，全是垃圾\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Absolutely, they're complete shit!
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.76,1:46:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的… - 面值是2億50萬\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}What's your.. what's your? - Face-value is 205 million
Dialogue: 0,1:46:58.06,1:46:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,美元\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Dollars
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.30,1:47:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們能…以40收購\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Alright, we could, we could go to forty
Dialogue: 0,1:47:01.94,1:47:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，至少要1億\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}No, we want at least a hundred million
Dialogue: 0,1:47:03.26,1:47:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,1個億？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}A hundred million?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.88,1:47:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你是毒品販子，還是搞銀行的？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Who are you a drug-dealer or a banker?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.16,1:47:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是銀行家，就立馬給我滾蛋\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Cause if you're a banker you can fuck right off!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.76,1:47:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道能不能坐莊，直接說你的最好報價\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I don't know if we can make a market, just give me your best price!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:12.06,1:47:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呦！1個億還嫌不夠\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Yeah, Check! a hundred million worth, and aim higher!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.82,1:47:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我覺得我們期望差太多\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I think we're far apart
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.58,1:47:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是不想買，就直接掛斷\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Look if you don't want to deal, just hang up.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:21.52,1:47:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我料想的一樣\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}That's what I thought!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.80,1:47:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,9千萬\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Ninety million
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.94,1:47:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,7千萬\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Seventy!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.16,1:47:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,8千5百萬\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Eighty-five
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.98,1:47:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 7千8百萬 - 8千4百萬\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Seventy-eight -Eighty-four!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.84,1:47:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 7千8百萬 - 8千4百萬\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Seventy-eight -Eighty-four!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.96,1:47:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我是貝利博士\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}It's Dr. Burry
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.70,1:47:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,看來金融危機馬上來了 （*全國斷供率超過12%）\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Looks like the collapse of the financial sector is imminent (*national default rates above 12 percent)
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.62,1:47:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我以現在的倉位出手\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Start to sell my position
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.88,1:47:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,23億\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}2.3 billion
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.12,1:47:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,當然，我可以等著\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Sure, I'll hold!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:51.06,1:47:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,* 親愛的勞倫斯\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}* Dear Lawrence
Dialogue: 0,1:47:52.26,1:47:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,* 你在賽恩資本的總盈利為4.89億\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}* Your profits totaling 489 million from Scion Capital
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.20,1:48:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,* 已經轉存到你的賬戶了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}* have been deposited into your account
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.20,1:48:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,* 不用謝。\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.50,1:48:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,* 德意志銀行紐約分行, 4千7百萬\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}*Deutsche bank new york. 47 million
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.88,1:48:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,最終我還是對的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}So I was right.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.22,1:48:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我被人噴了兩年…\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I took a rash of shit for two years. But...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.12,1:48:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我是對的\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I was right! And...
Dialogue: 0,1:48:20.54,1:48:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都錯了！\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Everyone was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:23.00,1:48:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我還拿到了獎金支票\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}And yeah i got a bonus-cheque for it
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.10,1:48:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,來告我啊\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Sue me!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.78,1:48:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,隨便了\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}You know.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:28.48,1:48:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,這錢是不少，我能感到你們心裡有看法\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}It's a lot of money! I get it, I can feel you judging me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:31.98,1:48:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,很明顯嘛\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}That's palpable
Dialogue: 0,1:48:34.02,1:48:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,可是呢\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}But hey!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.86,1:48:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我從沒說過我是這個故事裡的英雄人物\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}I never said I was the hero of this story
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.72,1:48:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你好啊\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}Hey, hey babe!
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.18,1:48:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,情況怎麼樣？\N{\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}How are we looking?
